{"tid":1443915,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【香城Online】工程兵發惡夢後研討 (防具升級篇)","createTime":"2019-08-11T10:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:07:12.000Z","uid":114192,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a4e8749e7970b9f9095013446c93925df67328d7","tid":1443915,"uid":114192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zByx77b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzByx77b.png&h=62196ab7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgYREd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgYREd4.png&h=37492541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.\t引言<br />\n<br />\n近排我地一班工程兵玩香城online，都會見到其他玩家俾怪物無差別攻擊。身為輔助兵種，我地會係呢個post提供一啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">升級裝備</span></span>嘅意見。<br />\n<br />\n防具最主要需求係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">防禦力</span></span>，其次就係對<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敏捷度</span></span>嘅影響、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入手容易度</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">舒適度</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n依家戰場上其實冇乜人有裝備<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盾牌</span></span>，就算有都只係路牌、薄木片、行李箱同水馬，被<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">怪物火槍兵</span></span>一射就爆。所以盾牌升級方向建議係加厚同利用夾層玻璃嘅概念（簡單啲講就係三文治）。將盾牌分為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3個夾層</span></span>，外層應該係最厚最硬嘅物料［圖中為三分(10mm)厚木板同埋層板（裝係書架嗰啲）］，用嚟抵擋攻擊；中間夾層就係加強盾牌耐久度同緩衝；內層就係再加強防禦力同加裝配件，下面會有一張簡單示意圖等玩家參考。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CR1WQkT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCR1WQkT.png&h=fba85129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.\t材料選擇<br />\n<br />\n2.1\t外層<br />\n只要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">夠厚夠硬</span></span>既材料就可以，但要留意會唔會超過玩家負重能力，最好連埋內層材料兩塊一齊拎起試一試重量<br />\n<br />\n2.2\t中間夾層<br />\n純玻璃膠<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒烤網加玻璃膠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n純玻璃膠優點係平少少，但因為缺少左燒烤網嘅增強作用，盾牌嘅耐久度同防禦力會較低，如果缺乏金錢先去考慮以純玻璃膠將上下兩層合二為一。必要嘅材料得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">玻璃膠</span></span>一種。可加配<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">膠槍</span></span>，但冇都可以製造到，只不過係慢啲同麻煩啲 (使用膠槍示範: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hwOJtFESKW8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhwOJtFESKW8&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKt5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=706d3f69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hwOJtFESKW8</a>)。購買膠槍前可以看搵一搵屋企裝備室有冇，大量製造或生活未算拮据可以購買。兩樣材料都可以係商城嘅五金舖購買到；<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nn8Vmsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNn8Vmsy.png&h=8a1265af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒烤網加玻璃膠，防禦性能會比只用玻璃膠高，而且<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒烤網</span></span>存在可以做到鋼筋(Reinforcement)嘅效果，加強盾牌嘅耐久度同防禦力高，但會貴少少同多兩重功夫，用時間同金錢換取防禦力，所以會比較建議用燒烤網加玻璃膠。<br />\n，即使外層被射穿，夾層嘅玻璃膠會減低子彈的威力。另一方面，燒烤網係商城嘅大型超市、百貨公司或者大型家品店都會搵到，以成本計推薦去家品店較佳。建議先定好盾牌尺寸再買燒烤網，否則有機會網大過板（又或需要額外裁剪）或者板大過網（防禦性能減低）既情況。<br />\n<br />\n2.3\t底層<br />\n如果外層好厚重，底層應該揀翻<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輕嘅物料</span></span>。但建議都要有一定硬度，起碼裝完配件唔會甩翻出嚟，而且可能會救到你一命，減少受傷情況。<br />\n<br />\n今次共整咗兩塊試驗作品，第一塊係外層同底層都係用三分(10mm)厚木板；而第二塊係外層用層板，底層用刺身砧板。<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示：玻璃膠咀位凸出部分要用𠝹刀批走少少先會唧到膠出嚟，如果有膠嘴嘅話膠嘴都要批走少少。但由於盾牌製作唔需要精密手工，唔建議使用膠嘴，可以更快速完成。<br />\n<br />\n配件方面參考怪物的輕盾兵嘅圓盾牌，握把同前臂帶係必須加配，否則俾怪物打兩下就會飛甩。所需材料可以係商城五金舖購入，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">安裝詳情可參考下面圖片簡介</span></span>。盾兵們可按個人需要，係唔減低防禦性能情況下，係盾牌加裝飾品。士氣Up!<br />\n<br />\n而盾牌嘅內則我地建議用返<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三點綁法</span></span>，同怪物嘅圓盾設計大同小異，以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩組小勾加尼龍繩或索帶</span></span>綁係前臂，最前位置加上<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">門抽</span></span>俾手指抓住，防止保護自己的過程中比怪物強力衝擊而去去武器走。"},{"pid":"02d8185509700f38b6a78566f590f36e32416dc9","tid":1443915,"uid":114192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"3.\tSamples<br />\n<br />\n3.1.\tSample 1 (<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">木板 &amp; 燒烤網 &amp; 玻璃膠</span></span>)<br />\n材料: \t\t木板x2 (木工舖, $80), 玻璃膠x2 (五金舖, $40),  燒烤網x1 (家品舖, $15), 鐵手抽x1 (五金舖, $6), 索帶<br />\n價錢: \t\t~$200<br />\n製作時間: \t~45mins<br />\n製作方法:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtsKZi0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtsKZi0.png&h=5888474b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dMWG1xp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdMWG1xp.png&h=9079eb95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Udn7cD4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUdn7cD4.png&h=3ddaf888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4mscD4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4mscD4.png&h=5cbee94b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/inxbEjv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FinxbEjv.png&h=0fa29d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZWDjjv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZWDjjv.png&h=93d6872f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHm0xEu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHm0xEu.png&h=1e58fff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5OcV5Zu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OcV5Zu.png&h=df7a667e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AfwvUTj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAfwvUTj.png&h=2d6ebe0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/maB4eTj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmaB4eTj.png&h=ddd132a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRQ8Gyk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRQ8Gyk.png&h=820fb93a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zzLwEj1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzzLwEj1.png&h=8a19e686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPUaarF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPUaarF.png&h=43bcd8ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後成品:</span></span>\t<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccWf5Wm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccWf5Wm.png&h=48239ff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.2.\tSample 2 (<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">層板 &amp; 砧板 &amp; 燒烤網 &amp; 玻璃膠</span></span>)<br />\n材料: \t\t層板x1 (家品舖, $81), 砧板x1 (家品舖, $68), 玻璃膠x1 (五金舖, $20),  燒烤網x1 (家品舖, $16), 大鐵手抽x1 (五金舖, $30), 索帶<br />\n價錢: \t\t~$200<br />\n製作時間: \t~45mins<br />\n製作方法:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rzyNW3q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrzyNW3q.png&h=b2daa828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MNM0xBL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMNM0xBL.png&h=7465623a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y386s96.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY386s96.png&h=1579dab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OVdBQoq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOVdBQoq.png&h=86e7d239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U6m7W3P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU6m7W3P.png&h=82e98a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P94mg3Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP94mg3Q.png&h=bea0569e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4gfXzQv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4gfXzQv.png&h=02b68695&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTKJvoQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTKJvoQ.png&h=cc7c4701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後成品:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tw6f5Xu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftw6f5Xu.png&h=fcf2003d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8RvUQP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8RvUQP.png&h=cb91765f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRemarks: \t以上係時間充足既情況下既製成品。但如果時間緊迫，玩家可以優先用索帶做綁前臂工具，另外提提玩家木板邊包返D膠紙唔好ݹ傷自己。總而言之之原理係整個木板三文治中間多醬最後包埋個邊就perfect。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩家需要其他相片 / 資訊，歡迎查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n. \t護具<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近期更新之後，開始出現左一啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">怪物棍手同刀手</span></span>，有見及此，我地可以再添置啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">護具</span></span>去增強我地嘅防禦力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n.1.\t<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">足球護脛</span></span><br />\n<br />\nimg]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/5G2ySMb.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5G2ySMb.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKt5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=e8643947\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/5G2ySMb.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n手場所:\t商城運動舖<br />\n<br />\n錢:\t\t$60 - $100<br />\n<br />\n點:\t\t外層嘅膠板可以提升防禦力，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">防止利器傷腳</span></span>，另外護脛背有緩衝用薄膠，可以吸收近攻型怪物嘅衝擊力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n.2. \t<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">防割傷手袖</span></span><br />\n<br />\nimg]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/rxeUCdc.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrxeUCdc.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKt5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=698f22b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/rxeUCdc.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n手場所:\t商城行山用品店<br />\n<br />\n錢:\t\t$40 - $60<br />\n<br />\n點:\t\t價錢親民，可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">增強對刀的抗性</span></span>，配合埋盾牌既就可以防禦到大部分嘅攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各路兄弟討伐成功。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8486f13cc938e650fa443270f6153f9222e704ff","tid":1443915,"uid":114192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:45:30.000Z","msg":"3.\tSamples<br />\n<br />\n3.1.\tSample 1 (<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">木板 &amp; 燒烤網 &amp; 玻璃膠</span></span>)<br />\n材料: \t\t木板x2 (木工舖, $80), 玻璃膠x2 (五金舖, $40),  燒烤網x1 (家品舖, $15), 鐵手抽x1 (五金舖, $6), 索帶<br />\n價錢: \t\t~$200<br />\n製作時間: \t~45mins<br />\n製作方法:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtsKZi0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtsKZi0.png&h=5888474b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dMWG1xp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdMWG1xp.png&h=9079eb95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Udn7cD4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUdn7cD4.png&h=3ddaf888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4mscD4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4mscD4.png&h=5cbee94b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/inxbEjv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=